      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Beyond K-12",
      "fontSize": 8.76030835444258,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Beyond K-12",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "yA9qIdrbkIzBItT3glLfm",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3488.049461955915,
      "y": -825.5092240263566,
      "width": 427.69896620821083,
      "height": 88.29533272283798,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "vAkgIIs1rXP0Bldee2Ta9"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b4i",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2111158635,
      "version": 1691,
      "versionNonce": 448975507,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1737655390154,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. Competetive Exams\nWe will host a nationwide JEE mock exam where students across India can take the exam at a\nscheduled time, replicating the actual JEE environment. This unique event will provide *All India\nRanking (AIR), offering students a clear benchmark for their performance among **20 lakh\nparticipants. Unlike other platforms, our *real-time, authentic ranking system will give a true\nreflection of their national standing. By partnering with leading coaching institutes on a revenue-\nsharing model, we aim to reach a large user base, providing valuable insights into students'\nreadiness for JEE and NEET, while building a strong, engaged community.",
      "fontSize": 8.829533272283793,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. Competetive Exams\nWe will host a nationwide JEE mock exam where students across India can take the exam at a scheduled time, replicating the actual JEE environment. This unique event will provide *All India Ranking (AIR), offering students a clear benchmark for their performance among **20 lakh participants. Unlike other platforms, our *real-time, authentic ranking system will give a true reflection of their national standing. By partnering with leading coaching institutes on a revenue-sharing model, we aim to reach a large user base, providing valuable insights into students' readiness for JEE and NEET, while building a strong, engaged community.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "j2TLZVUDQ9Js3q-PembQx",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3486.8422184647106,
      "y": -625.3109771972872,
      "width": 413.1893494915631,
      "height": 74.7930868019568,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "vAkgIIs1rXP0Bldee2Ta9"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b4j",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 424760331,
      "version": 1503,
      "versionNonce": 1586563123,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1737655390154,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "3. Data & API Selling\nWe will develop and sell APIs for educational data and AI models to other edtech\nplatforms, universities, or even corporate learning systems. These APIs could\nprovide access to models for personalized learning or intelligent content generation.\nUnlike existing platforms that are fragmented, we aim to be the UNIFIED\nEDUCATIONAL ECOSYSTEM.",
      "fontSize": 9.972411573594242,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "3. Data & API Selling\nWe will develop and sell APIs for educational data and AI models to other edtech platforms, universities, or even corporate learning systems. These APIs could provide access to models for personalized learning or intelligent content generation. Unlike existing platforms that are fragmented, we aim to be the UNIFIED EDUCATIONAL ECOSYSTEM.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "ODOj0Gc7PA3QRwH-_jFW9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3487.308066803218,
      "y": -721.2057324021566,
      "width": 423.3280653802205,
      "height": 83.35712039057144,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "vAkgIIs1rXP0Bldee2Ta9"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b4k",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 62954155,
      "version": 1439,
      "versionNonce": 575113683,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1737655390154,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "2. Personalized Mental Health Assistant\nWe don't just focus on academic learning; we also care about student’s emotions and\nmental well-being. While other platforms might offer basic study help, Misty looks at how\nyou're feeling and provides support like calming exercises, stress relief tips, or motivational\nmessages whenever you're struggling. It adapts to your emotional needs in real time,\nensuring you get the right help to stay both mentally healthy and focused on your\nstudies. This makes Misty a more holistic learning experience.",
      "fontSize": 9.526528044636736,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "2. Personalized Mental Health Assistant\nWe don't just focus on academic learning; we also care about student’s emotions and mental well-being. While other platforms might offer basic study help, Misty looks at how you're feeling and provides support like calming exercises, stress relief tips, or motivational messages whenever you're struggling. It adapts to your emotional needs in real time, ensuring you get the right help to stay both mentally healthy and focused on your studies. This makes Misty a more holistic learning experience.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
