      "updated": 1737657622734,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Key Features\n\n1. Multilingual Teaching (Hinglish)\n2. Cbse, Ncert, Dav, IB, Oxford, Icse support\n3. Pdf Upload, generate questions, ask doubts, learn\n4. Daily homework\n5. Notes of each chapter of each class\n6. PPts for dedicated topics\n7. Offline access, recorded video lessons\n8. VARK teaching model, displaying of graphics and notes while teaching, playing of sounds etc\n9. weekly tests\n10. Report of student's performance and test results via classroom app to parent\n\n",
      "fontSize": 7.445843043822822,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Key Features\n\n1. Multilingual Teaching (Hinglish)\n2. Cbse, Ncert, Dav, IB, Oxford, Icse support\n3. Pdf Upload, generate questions, ask doubts, learn\n4. Daily homework\n5. Notes of each chapter of each class\n6. PPts for dedicated topics\n7. Offline access, recorded video lessons\n8. VARK teaching model, displaying of graphics and notes while teaching, playing of sounds etc\n9. weekly tests\n10. Report of student's performance and test results via classroom app to parent\n\n",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
