      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Unique Value Propositions\n\n1. 24/7 Live Companion 🕰️\nClassroom offers 24/7 access to the AI tutors. This way, the student can learn and get help from\nanywhere, at any time. Be it homework or last minute exam preparation, Misty is there to guide them\nin detail, acting like your live companion\n\n2. Emotional Intelligence ❤️\nclassroom has the world's smartest emotional intelligent AI tutors. they have the ability to\nunderstand students' emotional states and react accordingly for a better learning experience. Based\non signs of stress, frustration, or disengagement, Tutors can personally support students in order\nto keep them motivated and calm in the learning process. Emotional well-being would then become\nbalanced with academic success.\n\n3. Real Time Feedback 📊\nClassroom gives real-time feedback during learning sessions and instantly identifies areas where the\nstudents are struggling and then gives them personalized suggestions for improvement. Whether it is\nthe academic performance or emotional well-being, Misty is sensitive to the student's progress and\nprovides immediate guidance, keeping them on track and continuously improving.\n\n4. True Personalization 🎯\nClassroom's actual personalization extends beyond the scope of all education tools since it\ndynamically varies both content and teaching approaches according to the strengths, weaknesses,\nand learning pace of each particular student. In contrast, whereas the other platforms just only\noffer static one-size fits all approaches, the AI tutors continuously analyzes student performance\nand, in real-time, ensures that lessons are always congruent with the needs of a student at present.\nUpon every class, Misty gives daily homework and does weekly tests. \n\n5. 95% Accurate Test Preparation 📝\nClassroom's test preparation is 95% accurate because it uses AI in the generation of question\npapers and practice tests that mimic the actual format of the exams, based on historical data and\ntrends. Misty uses past exams and current patterns to make sure the mock tests mirror the kind of\ndifficulty and questions they would face during the real exam, thereby giving a very realistic and\nhighly accurate view of how they might do. This helps the students focus their preparation on the\nright areas, thereby increasing the possibility of success in competitive exams.",
      "fontSize": 8.290666851875038,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Unique Value Propositions\n\n1. 24/7 Live Companion 🕰️\nClassroom offers 24/7 access to the AI tutors. This way, the student can learn and get help from anywhere, at any time. Be it homework or last minute exam preparation, Misty is there to guide them in detail, acting like your live companion\n\n2. Emotional Intelligence ❤️\nclassroom has the world's smartest emotional intelligent AI tutors. they have the ability to understand students' emotional states and react accordingly for a better learning experience. Based on signs of stress, frustration, or disengagement, Tutors can personally support students in order to keep them motivated and calm in the learning process. Emotional well-being would then become balanced with academic success.\n\n3. Real Time Feedback 📊\nClassroom gives real-time feedback during learning sessions and instantly identifies areas where the students are struggling and then gives them personalized suggestions for improvement. Whether it is the academic performance or emotional well-being, Misty is sensitive to the student's progress and provides immediate guidance, keeping them on track and continuously improving.\n\n4. True Personalization 🎯\nClassroom's actual personalization extends beyond the scope of all education tools since it dynamically varies both content and teaching approaches according to the strengths, weaknesses, and learning pace of each particular student. In contrast, whereas the other platforms just only offer static one-size fits all approaches, the AI tutors continuously analyzes student performance and, in real-time, ensures that lessons are always congruent with the needs of a student at present. Upon every class, Misty gives daily homework and does weekly tests. \n\n5. 95% Accurate Test Preparation 📝\nClassroom's test preparation is 95% accurate because it uses AI in the generation of question papers and practice tests that mimic the actual format of the exams, based on historical data and trends. Misty uses past exams and current patterns to make sure the mock tests mirror the kind of difficulty and questions they would face during the real exam, thereby giving a very realistic and highly accurate view of how they might do. This helps the students focus their preparation on the right areas, thereby increasing the possibility of success in competitive exams.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
